articles.description: Longtime NFL defensive coordinator Monte Kiffin died on Thursday at the age of 84, Ole Miss announced.
articles.headline: Longtime NFL DC Monte Kiffin dies at age 84

images.name: Monte Kiffin (March 27, 2024) [1296x729]
images.caption: Monte Kiffin, who spent 13 of his 16 seasons as an NFL defensive coordinator with the Buccaneers, is one of 15 recipients of the Pro Football Hall of Fame's Awards for Excellence.

articles.description: A U.S. appeals court, in the latest challenge to the NCAA's long-held notion of amateurism, said a test should be developed to differentiate between students who play college sports for fun and those whose effort "crosses the legal line into work."
